subject: The Big Billion Days Sale has begun!
body:
Don’t miss out—massive discounts on electronics, fashion, and home
essentials are now live. Shop quickly, the offers won’t last long!

subject: Poor support experience – need escalation
body:
Hi Team,
I’ve been trying to get assistance for several days regarding my claim, but
my issue remains unresolved. This delay is very disappointing. Please
escalate this matter urgently.
Regards.

subject: Please process my policy cancellation
body:
Hello,
I wish to discontinue my existing insurance policy. Kindly initiate the
cancellation and confirm once it has been successfully completed.
Thank you. Regards

subject: Premium payment issue – amount debited
body:
Hi Team,
I attempted to pay my premium online, but the transaction didn’t go through
while the amount was still deducted from my bank account. Please look into
this immediately and update me.
Regards.

subject: Need details on family health insurance plans
body:
Hello Support Team,
I’m planning to take a health insurance policy for my family and would like
to review the available options. Kindly share the plan benefits and premium
information.
Thank you. Regards

subject: Update needed on my hospital claim
body:
Hi Team,
I submitted my hospital claim last week and haven’t received any
communication since then. Could you please check the status and let me know
if it’s under process?
Thanks & Regards.

subject: It’s ON! Big Billion Days have officially started
body:
Deals are dropping fast! From smartphones to home appliances, everything is
up for grabs at unbelievable prices. Shop now before the best steals vanish!

subject: Need urgent escalation – unresolved claim issue
body:
Hi,
I’ve called your support team multiple times over the last few days, yet my
claim concern is still not addressed. The repeated lack of response is very
disappointing.
Please escalate this matter to the concerned department without delay.
Thank you. Regards

subject: Initiate cancellation of my policy
body:
Hello,
I would like to discontinue my current insurance policy due to personal
reasons. Please proceed with the cancellation and update me once the
process is completed.
Thank you for your support. Regards

subject: Premium payment issue – money deducted
body:
Hello,
I tried completing my premium payment through the online portal, but the
payment did not go through. Even though the transaction failed, the amount
has been deducted from my bank account.
Kindly look into this and advise on the next steps.
Regards.

subject: Looking for suitable health insurance options
body:
Hello Support Team,
I’m exploring health insurance plans for my family and would appreciate
some guidance. Could you please share the available policy options along
with their premiums and key benefits?
Thank you for your help. Regards

subject: Request for status on submitted hospital claim
body:
Hello,
I submitted my hospital claim last week and was expecting an acknowledgment
or update by now. May I please know the status and if any further
information is required from my side?
Regards.

subject: Big billion days sale now live
body:
Hurry up! Grab the best deals on electronics, fashion and home appliances.
Limited time offer!

subject: Very disappointed with your service
body:
This is extremely frustrating. I have been calling your support team for
the last 5 days and no one is helping me with my claim. This is very poor
service and I want to escalate this issue.

Very disappointed.

subject: Request to cancel my policy
body:
Hello Team,

I no longer wish to continue my insurance policy. Please cancel my policy
immediately and confirm the cancellation.

Regards.

subject: Premium payment failed but amount deducted
body:
Hi,

I tried paying my insurance premium online but the transaction failed.
However, the amount has already been deducted from my bank account. Please
resolve this issue urgently.

Thanks.

subject: Interested in buying new health insurance
body:
Hello Support,

I am planning to purchase a new health insurance policy for my family.
Please share the available plans and premium details.

Thank you.

subject: Claim status update required
body:
Hi Team,

I had submitted my hospital claim last week but haven’t received any update
yet. Please let me know the current status of my claim.

Regards.

subject: Policy request
body:
Hello,



I have misplaced my insurance policy documents. Please send me a soft copy
of my policy at the earliest.



Thanks.

subject: Policy paper
body:
Good afternoon sir,
This Is to request you for the asked policy, can you send those.
Yours sincerely,
Jack
